de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.measurement.kieker

Class KiekerMeasurementResultProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.measurement.kieker.KiekerMeasurementResultProcessor

  • public class KiekerMeasurementResultProcessor
extends Object
    Processes the results generated by Kieker and transforms them into corresponding measurement events. To do so, it needs one or multible CodeSectionIdentifiers. No events will be created for code sections that cannot be identified.
